abstract: After a promotion to creative director at Salvatore Ferragamo last month, Paul Andrew, fashion’s favorite shoe designer, has decided to put his own brand on ice.
snippet: After a promotion to creative director at Salvatore Ferragamo last month, Paul Andrew, fashion’s favorite shoe designer, has decided to put his own brand on ice.
lead_paragraph: What happens if you get a dream job, and it means giving up on your own name?

lead_paragraph: Over 2,000 students took us up on our second annual December challenge to “connect what you’re learning in school with the world today,” and, as you’ll see from the work of the winners, below, this year’s best were just as insightful and imaginative as last year’s.

abstract: Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada has been drawn into scandal around a corporation accused of corruption and his former justice minister, who said his office pressured her to drop the case.
snippet: Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada has been drawn into scandal around a corporation accused of corruption and his former justice minister, who said his office pressured her to drop the case.
lead_paragraph: TORONTO — Prime Minister Justin Trudeau of Canada promised a fresh approach to politics, one that was based on openness, decency and liberalism.

abstract: New research documents the far-reaching effects of the cash bail system, which disproportionately hurts the poor and African-Americans.
snippet: New research documents the far-reaching effects of the cash bail system, which disproportionately hurts the poor and African-Americans.
lead_paragraph: Cash bail favors the rich, who can pay it and go home, while poorer people are frequently forced to remain in jail while they await trial.
